Doc: A value of the adjustment point, consisting of the x value and the corresponding y value.

Source.Contents:
/#
   A value of the adjustment point, consisting of the x value and the corresponding y value.
 #/
record FpML5.reporting.ParametricAdjustmentPoint {
  # The value of the independent variable (e.g. strike offset).
  parameterValue : decimal?

  # The value of the dependent variable, the actual adjustment amount.
  adjustmentValue : decimal?

}

parameterValue.Doc: The value of the independent variable (e.g. strike offset).
parameterValue.Name: parameterValue

adjustmentValue.Doc: The value of the dependent variable, the actual adjustment amount.
adjustmentValue.Name: adjustmentValue
